{
  "stem": "7437.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I think the goal of the Germans, to rob us of all the dignity that was left at the time, did-- the Germans accomplished it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't have any connection with the outside world.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was no mail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were no newspapers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were no radios.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Just we were left to our own devices.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, I was a little over 10, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, a little over 10 years of age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'41.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How could I have been 12?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "December '29.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just about.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, not quite.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My arithmetic is not very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stayed in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everyone who worked, over 14 years of age, received a very small ration.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Under 14 years of age, one didn't work, and consequently didn't get any food at all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my mother and my sister shared their small rations with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Children like myself were left during the day with nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a whole group of children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We got together and we dug a hole.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I call it a tunnel, but it was not a tunnel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a hole.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we made a way of getting out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm proud to say that none of the children ever gave hole away or denounced it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We would sneak out in the middle of the day and remove our yellow stars, and try to either beg or buy some kind of food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I want to trace back a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In the beginning of the ghetto, my mother and several other women were also able-- or they established a clandestine school for children like myself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that school existed for several months in the evenings after the women came back from work.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
